parameters:
\SE[2]Welcome... I welcome you. \SE[1]Since the incident in
Elmo Village, right?

\SE[2]It is an honor to be granted an audience, King Cordin.
\!\SE[3]...I believe you already know the purpose of our
visit.

\SE[3]You know everything, don't you? \!\SE[0]Did you come
to stop me... no, \!\SE[2]did you come to kill me?

\SE[32]... If it is necessary. \!\SE[3] May I ask you one
thing?

\SE[3]There are things you don't understand, huh?
\SE[2]Alright. Go ahead and ask.

\SE[2]What is the reason for gathering Rare Earth to such an
excessive extent? \SE[3]It seems too much for the purpose of
maintaining the country... Where is the objective?

\SE[3]Huh? You understood that much from that document?
\SE[2]...You're really clever.

\SE[3]Do you know...? Occasionally, there are cracks in the
world, and beyond them... the existence of a world unknown
to us.

\SE[8]Currently... we have not yet interfered with that
world.

\SE[15]In my opinion... that is a timeline of the future.
\SE[0]It seems that humans have a civilization that utilizes
our unimaginable technology.

\SE[13]Surely, beyond that, there is unknown technology that
surpasses us... \SE\SE[1]A future that will completely
overturn this world that is completely dependent on fossil
fuels... \SE[1]It must exist.

\SE[15]However, opening a rift requires an enormous amount
of energy. Even with the power of magic... it is beyond
reach. \SE[14]...That's why I decided to do it.

\SE[15]Gathering fuel from the entire land... and burning it
in the most powerful way. \SE[2]This way, we can generate
energy that surpasses magic.

\SE[13]Just a little... I tried it. \!\SE[15]I opened a very
large hole... \!\SE[14]And caused an explosion.
\SE[1]I was able to open the entrance.

\SE[11]However... it seems that delicate adjustments are
necessary. \!\SE[14]I ended up breaking a little bit of the
other side.

\SE[11]What spread out was a cracked world.
\SE[12]Unfortunately, I couldn't obtain the... ideal results
that I was seeking.

\SE[15]Just one step... \!\SE[12]I couldn't reach the point
of interference.

\SE[14]Even so, just a little more... \SE[15]If we continue
to burn more and more fuel... I'm sure we will reach it.

\SE\SE\SE[1]Aren't you excited, Lunaroa? \SE\SE[1]The
possibility of us being able to open a door that will
decisively change history... It's like a dream.

\SE[15]However, it requires national power, financial
resources, and strong determination. \SE[2]It's not
something that someone else could do for us... \SE[2]I
decided that I will see it through to the end.

\SE\SE[2]That's why, for the sake of my own beliefs, I will
never stop. \.No matter how much sacrifice it may require.
\!\SE[2]

\SE[6]It got a little long, didn't it? \SE[1]I wonder if it
answered your question.

\SE[6]I'm sure... I wanted to hear your thoughts too.
\SE[1]It seems like I ended up talking too much.

\SE[32]...I understand your thoughts well. \SE[3]It's a
different path from ours.

\SE[5]Well... Shall we? During the research process...
Various powers were born. \SE[14]I'm eager to show you, so I
can't sit still.

\SE[12](...Let's go, Laura. \SE[0]It's okay. If you're with
me, I can become stronger no matter where we go.)

\SE[13]... It seems like I've returned to my childhood, I'm
excited... \SE[2] Fill my boredom... Lunaroa...!!

\SE[3]...You're really amazing. It's even beyond what the
chairman said.

\SE[0]If you were on my side... we might have been able to
shorten it by 30 years. \SE[3]It's a little... frustrating.

\SE[3]... Will she awaken? \!\SE[14] I wonder if she has
been captivated by the battle...?

\SE[15]Oh... 'Alice of Knowledge'. To think that I can see
it with my own eyes... \SE[2]I wonder if... if she can
understand me...?
\SE[2]You... are the one who called me?

\SE[15]That's right... Won't you show me a new future in
this world...?

\SE[2]... Huh? You're not dying? \. That's amazing, big
sister. \!\SE[1] Tell me. Your name.
\SE[47]I am Lunaroa. \SE[3]May I ask who you are...?

\SE[5]I am 'Alice'. \SE[3]But you can call me 'Alice of
Knowledge'... \SE[1]It's a bit long, so just 'Alice' is
fine.

\SE[2]Yes, thank you. 'Alice'... What a lovely name. \SE[3]I
wonder why you came here?

\SE[2]Why...? \.Is it because I was called by the person I
just killed...? \!\SE[3]I'm just looking for 'Mama'.
\SE[2] Mama...? Are you looking for your mother?

\SE[3]... That's enough, right? I'm bored. \SE[5] Big
sister, play with me like earlier.

\SE[2]Can you take me with you too? \.Is it unfair that it's
only me?
\SE[2]I also... wanted to play with this person...

\SE\SE[0]Oh, by the way... Could you... become my Mama?
\.Wouldn't that be wonderful...? \!\SE[0]What do you think?

\SE\SE[15]I thought so after all...? \SE[15]That's
great...\.Then it's settled.

\SE\SE[15]Hehe... Because that child gets lonely easily...
Please love them a lot, okay? \SE[15]Take care of them... as
their Mama, okay?

\SE[17]No way!! This place is collapsing! \SE[15]We need to
escape quickly...!

\SE[18]R-Right...! \.You take care of Laura! \!\SE[22]I'll
carry Lunaroa!!
